{
  "texts": [
    "Phylogenetic analysis of RGAs in Ae. tauschii.",
    "To provide further evidence for the homology of the SrTA1662 (SR66) and SR33 loci in Ae.",
    "tauschii and the Mla locus in barley, we performed phylogenetic analyses of RGA and RGH gene sequences.",
    "Clustal algorithm with default parameters was used for the DNA sequence multiple alignment.",
    "We used the unweighted UPGMA algorithm with bootstrap testing to support the tree topology with 5,000 replicates."
  ]
}